Mix together the cocoa, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, and pinch of salt in a saucepan. Blend in the boiling water. Bring this mixture to an easy boil while you stir. Simmer, and stir for about 2 minutes. Watch that it doesn't scorch. Stir in 3 1/2 cups of milk and heat until very hot, but do not boil! Remove from heat, and add vanilla. Divide between 4 mugs. Pour 2 tablespoons half-and-half into each mug of cocoa , and serve.